	</div><div class='btext_mm' style='padding: 2px; overflow: auto; width:510; word-wrap:break-word; margin: 0px 8px;'>OTTi RO is highly compelling option for players looking for a Ragnarok Zero or Revo-Classic style experience, especially those with busy real-life schedules. The server offer great stability with excellent 24/7 uptime, meaning you rarely have to worry about random disconnects or lag.

The most unique aspect of this server is its build-in auto attack feature.</div><div id='revinfo' style='height: 16px;'>
