		Midgard Tales - 200x/200x/20x</a></div><div style='padding: 2px; border-bottom: 2px solid #38719C; margin: 0px 5px;'>
		<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
			<tr class='switch'>
				<td width=140> &nbsp; <a href = 'index.php?page=userprofile&uid=272562' class = 'rev_sw' >xwing141991</a></td>
				<td width=115><div style='width: 110; height: 20; background: url(images/overall.gif) repeat-x 0 0;'><!-- empty --></div></td>
				<td width=180 align='center'>Played for more than 1 year</td>
				<td width=70 align='right'>2026-05-28</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</div><div class='btext_mm' style='padding: 2px; overflow: auto; width:510; word-wrap:break-word; margin: 0px 8px;'>I have played the server 2 years ago and stopped playing bec of personal matters. When I decided to return, I was at first overwhelmed with the number of new features in the game but luckily, GM LAI is very helpful, kind and patient that directed to me to what I need to do first. The community in game might not be the same as before but we have a GM that compensates that. I freaking love the auto play feature lmao this server is solid 10/10 and I just found myself grinding again after 2 years</div><div id='revinfo' style='height: 16px;'>
		<div style='width:150px; float:left;'>			
			<img src="images/plus.gif" onClick="expandcontent(this, 'expand221879')"/>
