	<br><div id='review' style='margin: auto;'><div class='review-BL-top'><!-- empty --></div><div class='review-BL-mid'><div style='padding: 3px 0 3px 5px; border-bottom: 2px solid #38719C; text-align: left; margin: 0px 5px;'><img src = 'images/circle.gif'><a href = '/index.php?page=detailedlistserver&serid=22523&url_sname=Oldschool RO - Midrate' class='sb_m' >
		Oldschool RO - Midrate - 150x/150x/2500x</a></div><div style='padding: 2px; border-bottom: 2px solid #38719C; margin: 0px 5px;'>
		<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
			<tr class='switch'>
				<td width=140> &nbsp; <a href = 'index.php?page=userprofile&uid=272559' class = 'rev_sw' >AnimaROm</a></td>
				<td width=115><div style='width: 28; height: 20; background: url(images/overall.gif) repeat-x 0 0;'><!-- empty --></div></td>
				<td width=180 align='center'>Played for 3 months</td>
				<td width=70 align='right'>2026-05-27</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</div><div class='btext_mm' style='padding: 2px; overflow: auto; width:510; word-wrap:break-word; margin: 0px 8px;'>A severely pinoy infested server. GMs are mostly pinoys too and they dont really care about player relations.

Server is practically running itself to the ground, as we have seen before many times in other pinoy infested servers.

KS and PK are everywhere. No way to turn it off effectively and no way to get some proper training done.

Trolls are rude pinoy folks are everywhere. Friendliness on this server is practically a myth else theyre just putting on a show for new comers.

Do not recommend.</div><div id='revinfo' style='height: 16px;'>
		<div style='width:150px; float:left;'>			
			<img src="images/plus.gif" onClick="expandcontent(this, 'expand221878')"/>
