	<br><div id='review' style='margin: auto;'><div class='review-BL-top'><!-- empty --></div><div class='review-BL-mid'><div style='padding: 3px 0 3px 5px; border-bottom: 2px solid #38719C; text-align: left; margin: 0px 5px;'><img src = 'images/circle.gif'><a href = '/index.php?page=detailedlistserver&serid=23087&url_sname=Ragnarok+' class='sb_m' >
		Ragnarok+ - 2x/2x/1x</a></div><div style='padding: 2px; border-bottom: 2px solid #38719C; margin: 0px 5px;'>
		<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>
			<tr class='switch'>
				<td width=140> &nbsp; <a href = 'index.php?page=userprofile&uid=272557' class = 'rev_sw' >Craymel</a></td>
				<td width=115><div style='width: 98; height: 20; background: url(images/overall.gif) repeat-x 0 0;'><!-- empty --></div></td>
				<td width=180 align='center'>Played for 2 months</td>
				<td width=70 align='right'>2026-05-27</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</div><div class='btext_mm' style='padding: 2px; overflow: auto; width:510; word-wrap:break-word; margin: 0px 8px;'>Interesting server with lots of QoL changes. Every class got some improvements, but some are lacking imo. Many mobs drop their hats. They nicely integrated Hardcore and Softcore (regular) characters &amp; they typically can't interest with each other besides talking/walking. No WoE yet but eventually coming. Reputation system with many hunting quests gives long-term content for the game. Vending is great. Some custom items/mobs/dungeons too each with a story. Certainly not perfect but a fun server.</div><div id='revinfo' style='height: 16px;'>
		<div style='width:150px; float:left;'>			
			<img src="images/plus.gif" onClick="expandcontent(this, 'expand221877')"/>
